The wiki page on AVL trees mention that:

&gt; The retracing can stop if the balance factor becomes 0 implying that the height of that subtree remains unchanged.

However, I am unable to see why this is the case when a LR/RL rotation potentially requires propagating the update of `balance_factor` values beyond such a node. 

